“Do you do this often?” she asked desperately.
He lowered his phone, circling it to indicate the car. “What, this?
Travel? No, not as often as I used to. Why?”
“I had no idea you were such a morning person.”
“It was all those morning swim meets in high school and college. I got
used to being an early riser, burning off all that extra energy before dawn in
