“We promote based on merit, not tenure. Otherwise, people think they
deserve a raise just for showing up.” A harsh edge snaked into his voice.
“Wouldn’t I be working directly under you then?”
Nicholas paused, and Jay cringed inwardly, her eyes instinctively
