He must have seen the newspaper, too. “It’s been nine years.”
“So? Nobody can hold a grudge like Nick. Hell, he’ll fuck with you for
fun, just to show you he can. Just like his dad used to do with his investors.
He learned that from his old man.”
This was a little too close to the truth and it made Jay’s jaw clench.
