the side of the house, and after spending a few hours going through the
footage, he’d caught a glimpse of a stealthy figure making its way up the
walkway. They hesitated for only a moment before heading not towards the
front door, but to the immediate left. Right for the pool.
Like they knew exactly where to go.
Jay, the poor little bird, thought this was going to ruin their lives.
Thinking, no doubt, of the men like his father who would only be too happy
