“I told you what I was willing to do to make you mine.”
Jay applied the Q-tip from hell to his face far more viciously than he
felt the situation required. “Have you ever read Faust, Nicholas?”
“Why? Is it hot?”
“Stop smiling. This isn’t funny.”
Oh, Jay, you’re having far too much fun topping Daddy from the
bottom in his own home.
He wound his arm around her waist and tugged her bodily onto his lap.
Startled, she fumbled with the bottle of rubbing alcohol and nearly dropped
