really did tell her about what had been doing on between us.”
Jay shook her head desperately. “Oh god. I don’t want her having that
kind of hold on me, Nicholas. She knows I gave up the money for you.”
“Nothing is going to happen to you.”
“It already has! For years, I searched my name, waiting for the ticking
